# Pronoun sets a player can choose from, one per line: a label, then in parentheses the five slash-separated forms
# (subject / object / possessive determiner / possessive pronoun / reflexive) that drive how third-person messages
# refer to that player. Blank lines and lines starting with a hash are ignored. Edit while the server is stopped.
Masculine/male (he/him/his/his/himself)
Feminine/female (she/her/her/hers/herself)
Singular/they (they/them/their/theirs/themself)
It/non binary (it/it/its/its/itself)
Ze/hir (ze/hir/hir/hirs/hirself)
Ze/zir (ze/zir/zir/zirs/zirself)
Xe/xem (xe/xem/xyr/xyrs/xemself)
Ey/em (ey/em/eir/eirs/emself)
Fae/faer (fae/faer/faer/faers/faerself)
None/unknown (name only)
